# Privacy Policy - BettingTips

**Last updated:** October 31, 2024

## Introduction
BettingTips ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data when you use our mobile application.

## Information We Collect

### Personal Information
- Email address (for authentication)
- Name (optional, for personalization)
- Betting preferences and history
- Device information (device type, OS version)

### Automatically Collected Information
- App usage analytics (via Firebase Analytics)
- Crash reports (via Firebase Crashlytics)
- Performance data

## How We Use Your Information
- To provide and maintain our service
- To notify you about changes to our service
- To provide customer support
- To gather analysis or valuable information to improve our service
- To detect, prevent and address technical issues

## Data Storage
- Your data is stored securely using Firebase services
- We use industry-standard encryption
- Data is stored on servers located in [YOUR REGION]

## Data Sharing
We do NOT sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties, except:
- Service providers (Firebase, Google Analytics) who help us operate our app
- When required by law

## Your Rights
You have the right to:
- Access your personal data
- Correct inaccurate data
- Request deletion of your data
- Opt-out of analytics tracking

## Children's Privacy
Our service is not intended for children under 18 years of age.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
- Email: mtngnr7@gmail.com
- Website: https://bettingtips.com/contact

